entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Obsève yo, voye je sou yo? Sa nap jwenn lè nou fè sa?" t="Observe them? What we gonna get from observing them?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ti mamay Zoe yo ap flannen bò gwo wou a ankò." t="Zoe's kid is hanging around dat rollercoaster again." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou genyen yon pi bon lide? Ale jwen moun Batty yo epi di yo sak pou fèt." t="You got a better idea? Then go to Batty's and tell dem." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="E pi? Ki pwoblèm sa bay?" t="And? What's wrong with dat?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Li ka pa la, li deyò, lap chèche djòb." t="He could be out trying to find a job" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa ta ka rive ou tou." t="It could happen to you too." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se pa djòb mwen pou mwen di yo sa yo gen pou fè. " t="It's not my place to tell them what to do." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa enève m pou wè bann Zannimo gen tout libète pou fè sa vle." t="It just pisses me off that Animals have a free pass to do whatever dey want." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Epi nou sipoze chita epi gade." t="And we're just supposed to sit and watch." b="" a=""/>
